{"tid":1279653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[必睇，請廣傳］Twitter私隠設置你要睇","createTime":"2019-07-02T17:16:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T00:29:11.000Z","uid":19408,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"53727fa4e21e7f0d01f9cb978733a3dd36e4044a","tid":1279653,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:16:48.000Z","msg":"一丶防止黑警白撞<br />\nTwitter如果你要改密碼，可以重設但係Menu上面會顯示你電話同電郵一部分，咁黑警就可以白撞再縮小範圍查你<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z3ipmMw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ3ipmMw.png&h=8124db52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZXfK6dc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZXfK6dc.png&h=86969b10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EhFK6dd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEhFK6dd.png&h=a33d2c44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開重設保護<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HpgKmMz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHpgKmMz.png&h=7fc0d461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁黑警們就無得白撞你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時，關埋掃尋功能，防止白撞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GYOXGMz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGYOXGMz.png&h=6ce9bd5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U6SUJZV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU6SUJZV.png&h=93b6749e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n二丶電郵服務<br />\n如果大家覺得Gmail仍然唔可靠，可以用Protonmail。呢個電郵堪稱世界數一數二安全，連斯諾登都用佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b69e4d732cfdd8d621d7ca1e61ffc41dd1be6b6c","tid":1279653,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:17:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.基本上Twitter繁簡中圈反共辱支丶甚至支持香港人比率十分高，反五毛反支生態差唔多已經支配咗成個Twitter<br />\n<br />\n2.Twitter差唔多隔一段時間就有五毛俾人打到身份證就俾人起底，五毛要容身根本唔及Facebook易<br />\n<br />\n所以，大家加油，放心去做！</span>"},{"pid":"5229b4e42d347b4844628f87cd9221c6dddb3f61","tid":1279653,"uid":19408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b69e4d732cfdd8d621d7ca1e61ffc41dd1be6b6c","tid":1279653,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:17:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.基本上Twitter繁簡中圈反共辱支丶甚至支持香港人比率十分高，反五毛反支生態差唔多已經支配咗成個Twitter<br />\n<br />\n2.Twitter差唔多隔一段時間就有五毛俾人打到身份證就俾人起底，五毛要容身根本唔及Facebook易<br />\n<br />\n所以，大家加油，放心去做！</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:18:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">首先，最重要：<br />\n@lihkg_forum</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">知已知彼，百戰百勝</span><br />\n支那反五毛群體：<br />\n@real_zhinared<br />\n@Zhinawiki<br />\n@Linmeng1919810<br />\n@SmzdBan<br />\n@zhangxianzhong<br />\n<br />\n釣魚：<br />\n@SZ_CyberPolice<br />\n@Xhnsoc_Redflag<br />\n@WaFangDianPF<br />\n@NationSafeCNWeb<br />\n@RedStarTimes<br />\n<br />\n反共名人Bot：<br />\n@MaoTseTungBot<br />\n@Jiangqingbot2<br />\n@luxunbot25<br />\n@liuxiaobobot<br />\n@hushihbot<br />\n<br />\n辱華名人：<br />\n@bilishe<br />\n@wohuijide[/quote]"},{"pid":"22adb27880a49de2f7505ba03d186a28b26cd751","tid":1279653,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:18:49.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"b423588c2c3e53a484628cf92ec40f40a0bc9706","tid":1279653,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:19:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d408cafa1cf2162a9fc097f2bf1d87c06c7f5659","tid":1279653,"uid":19408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T17:19:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"462d211397410a635f69518afa31f1e0130d15c2","tid":1279653,"uid":19408,